    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/dfeae08ed063b2577263f678e406358e.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=222 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/9502cc1328c5cdded044a21a8418dc71.poster.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/9502cc1328c5cdded044a21a8418dc71.webm?t=1755091544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>与最多 16 名玩家进行在线游戏.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/54008f2871528f47a796b51feb7b4a1d.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=222 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/affb85b48b681aa4fb4ff4c582bdb3cc.poster.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/affb85b48b681aa4fb4ff4c582bdb3cc.webm?t=1755091544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>一切皆可用作武器，用力掷出所有道具，造成毁天灭地的大破坏！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/5159ee7f62972efd9c7e5f48328314fd.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=222 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/f7fdb04e21e3f14c7e9520d9620af391.poster.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/f7fdb04e21e3f14c7e9520d9620af391.webm?t=1755091544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>在各种癫狂混乱的游戏模式中制霸全场。我们还会不断加入新地图、游戏模式和奖励！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/863119cc204c4d81af401013f4f74143.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=222 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/410a1f0a28298bdb78d330d1bfe26b47.poster.avif?t=1755091544\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307870/extras/410a1f0a28298bdb78d330d1bfe26b47.webm?t=1755091544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>造成伤害、积攒怒气，你的角色就会越变越大！你可以自定义角色，并且可以解锁海量角色皮肤！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >加入这场肉搏，在热血的战斗盛宴中战个痛快！肆意疯狂，肆意爆发，肆意杀戮！</h2><br>现在将 OutRage:Fight Fest 加入愿望单，即可了解最新的开发进度，并在游戏推出时第一时间收到通知。此外，加入我们的  频道，即有机会参与内部游戏测试，帮助我们让游戏变得更好。<br><br>如果你喜欢《猛兽派对》的基于物理特性互动玩法，并且希望玩到规模更大、更具深度的战斗，或者喜欢《Stumble Guys》的疯狂多人游戏，那么 OutRage:Fight Fest 就适合你！",
